body.name: AZDOME 4K Dash Cam 5G WiFi GPS, WDR Super Night Vision Camera for Car, G-Sensor, Parking Mode, Free 64GB SD Card, 170° Wide Angle Dashcam, Loop Recording, Voice Control M300S
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Wednesday, February 21. Order within 1 hr 22 mins
features: Dual-Channel Dash Cam: AZDOME front and rear dash cam records video of up to 4K (3840*2160P)+1080P resolutions, ensuring that license plates, road signs, and any other critical details are accurately captured.

Excellent Night Vision: Equipped with the F1.8 aperture and WDR tech, the dash cam automatically corrects the color balance and ensures high-quality images. No more worrying about blurry recordings at night.

Voice/App Control: With built-in 5G WiFi, you can connect this dash cam to your Android or iOS phone. Using the AZDOME app, you can view, download, share the videos and more. Additionally, it supports your spoken commands, like lock video, take photos, turn WiFi on/off, etc.

G-Sensor & Accident Lock: The dash cam will auto lock and save the emergency video when a sudden collision is detected on the road. It also supports a 24-hour parking monitor to record continuously for 24 hours with time lapse function at parking mode. Please note that an extra hardware kit is needed.

Loop Recording & Free 64GB Card: AZDOME dash cam won't lose any crucial evidence with loop recording function, overwriting the oldest unprotected files when the SD card is about full. Rest assured that a 64GB SD card is included in the package.
Hassle-free Warranty: AZDOME dash cam is covered by a 12-month warranty and lifetime technical supports. Please feel free to contact us with any problems.

reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the 4K Dash Cam 5G WiFi GPS, and I am thrilled with its performance. Additionally, the convenient parking feature offers round-the-clock surveillance, safeguarding my vehicle while it's parked. Overall, this dash cam is a remarkable device that surpasses my expectations and provides an unparalleled sense of security on the road.
